    </div>
  </div></section>

  <!-- LEAGUE STARTER PACK -->
  <section class="starter bleed"><div class="wrap">
    <div>
      <span class="ey">League Starter Pack</span>
      <span class="rule"></span>
      <h2 class="t">Build a Mug Set for the Whole League</h2>
      <p class="sub">Send us your league name and theme. We create 3 custom design options, include up to 3 revision rounds, and produce a minimum set of 8 mugs for your league.</p>
      <div class="starter-badge">
        <span>8 Mug Minimum &nbsp;·&nbsp; 3 Design Options &nbsp;·&nbsp; 3 Revision Rounds</span>
      </div>
      <div class="starter-steps">
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-n">01</div>
          <div class="step-t">Tell Us Your League</div>
          <div class="step-d">Name, theme, sport, year, inside jokes</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-n">02</div>
          <div class="step-t">Get 3 Custom Designs</div>
          <div class="step-d">Built around your league identity</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-n">03</div>
          <div class="step-t">3 Revision Rounds</div>
          <div class="step-d">Until it feels exactly like yours</div>
        </div>
        <div class="step">
          <div class="step-n">04</div>
          <div class="step-t">Mugs for Everyone</div>
          <div class="step-d">Every manager gets their mug</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="starter-cta">
        <a class="btn btn-gold" href="#newsletter">Join the Waitlist</a>
        <a class="btn btn-out" href="/pages/contact">Tell Us About Your League</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="starter-fig">
      <img src="{{ p_league.featured_image | image_url: width: 500 }}" alt="Custom league mug pack">
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <!-- ROAST -->
  <section class="roast bleed"><div class="wrap">
    <div class="fig"><img src="{{ p_sacko.featured_image | image_url: width: 500 }}" alt="Last Place Toilet Bowl Sacko mug"></div>
    <div>
      <span class="ey">The Roast · Anti-Trophy</span>
      <h2>Last Place Deserves a Monument Too.</h2>
      <span class="rule"></span>
      <p>The Sacko, the Toilet Bowl, the Participation Trophy: tarnished-bronze designs built to remind your league's worst manager of exactly where they finished. No gold here. Gold is for winners.</p>
      <a class="btn btn-tarn" href="/collections/the-sacko">Shop The Roast</a>
    </div>
  </div></section>

  <!-- NEWSLETTER -->
  <section class="nl bleed" id="newsletter"><div class="wrap">
    <span class="ey">Draft Season Alerts</span><span class="rule c"></span>
    <h2 class="t">Get $5 Off Your First Mug</h2>
    <p>New designs every season, plus early access before your draft. No spam, just trophies and trash talk.</p>
    {% form 'customer' %}
      <input type="hidden" name="contact[tags]" value="newsletter">
      <input type="email" name="contact[email]" placeholder="you@league.com" required>
      <button type="submit" class="btn btn-gold">Join</button>
    {% endform %}
  </div></section>

</div>

